'''Greentree Pointe''' was a family-oriented resort island on [[Dorumaa]] attracting wealthy customers. It was located thirty degrees north of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] equator. Its concierge in [[31 BBY/Legends|31 BBY]] was [[El'Tar Miskin]].<ref name="LFC">''[[Living Force Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

